dcterms:description: The Keto-Med dataset is a randomized crossover trial that placed participants on two different low-carb diets, Ketogenic and Mediterranean, targeting adults from the San Francisco Bay area with Type-2 diabetes or prediabetes. The dataset includes controlled meals during the first four weeks and self-reported diet adherence for the last eight weeks, capturing challenges such as missing meals and inaccurate meal information.
dcterms:title: Keto-Med dataset
